Falcon,is,a,video,game,and,combat,flight,simulator,that,provides,a,realistic,simulation,of,piloting,an,F,Fighting,Falcon,jet,fighter,The,FalconLog,website,provides,Falcon,pilots,with,a,place,to,upload,their,logbooks,The,site,stores,the,data,online,so,that,users,can,see,their,progress,over,time,along,with,detailed,statistics,that,go,beyond,what,the,simulator,itself,shows,The,site,supports,multiple,versions,of,Falcon,including,Allied,Force,Benchmarksim,BMS,Free,Falcon,and,Open,Falcon,The,logbook,service,can,be,accessed,programmatically,via,SOAP,API